{"tid":1078077,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瘋狂機師偷飛機撞俱樂部圖殺妻","createTime":"2019-03-26T04:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T05:35:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8865415ae9b68c251386ebce175bb4faa1d54b85","tid":1078077,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:45:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190326/20641572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F20641572&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhsSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=435550af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F20641572&h=7f2f0d3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190326/20641572</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瘋狂機師偷飛機撞俱樂部圖殺妻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190326/large/26wh105p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190326%2Flarge%2F26wh105p.jpg&h=fb3ad1e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑為殺妻的機師事前多次在俱樂部上空低飛。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n非洲南部國家博茨瓦納（Botswana）一名機師上周六偷去小型飛機後，連人帶機撞向正有包括他妻子在內60人舉行派對的飛行俱樂部，懷疑想殺妻的38歲機師維喬安（Charl Viljeon）送院後證實不治，相信無其他人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190326/large/26wh106p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190326%2Flarge%2F26wh106p.jpg&h=c2b7ed25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飛機撞向俱樂部後引發大火，機師連人帶機墜毀身亡。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190326/large/26wh107p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190326%2Flarge%2F26wh107p.jpg&h=d5ccf966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n維喬安（左）與妻子娜塔莎。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引發大火機師亡<br />\n<br />\n俱樂部位於首都嘉柏隆里（Gaborone）附近的馬吉延（Matsieng），目擊者指維喬安事發前不請自來到迎嬰聚會現場，毆打與他育有一子的妻子娜塔莎。據了解他之後前往以南約48公里的塞雷茨．卡馬爵士國際機場，未經同意下自行駛走一部可載八人的雙螺旋槳小型飛機B200。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者指飛機撞向俱樂部前曾多次飛過現場，狀似恐嚇在場人士。另有目擊者表示，機師於事發前曾致電一名朋友確認妻子仍在現場。最後飛機以高速低飛撞向俱樂部後引發大火，俱樂部大樓、13部汽車和航空交通管制塔受損。<br />\n<br />\n馬吉延飛行俱樂部確認當時場地正舉行私人派對，聲明指「下午約6時15分飛機從機場方向飛往馬吉延小型飛機場，多次在上空低飛徘徊。俱樂部會員懷疑機師別有用心，即疏散約60名在場人士」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n脫歐協議倘通過 文翠珊或願辭職<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n新西蘭總理徹查槍擊案起因"},{"pid":"75d55d743ad22e53aefd26213d33abf17689c5bf","tid":1078077,"uid":182178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:47:51.000Z","msg":"這樣做對他有甚麼好處"},{"pid":"a139e045767ee98e1d118f578e110366bfddda98","tid":1078077,"uid":141330,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:50:59.000Z","msg":"前世一定係日本仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9e4e4ba088cdce333c9706bac08225fe0c9e31","tid":1078077,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:52:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"424e019dcd18ca13411d0404286af5186bc03494","tid":1078077,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:05:28.000Z","msg":"要自殺就應該要咁"},{"pid":"8a563a21986830e7aa0750e7e50b3025f5da9ea1","tid":1078077,"uid":106233,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:06:19.000Z","msg":"神風敢死隊"},{"pid":"35071b11eaaeec5ff0b36695e40a813ff662306e","tid":1078077,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:06:38.000Z","msg":"gta <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b84ecfc4a33539ffb421b8a55f4b6e8ae35529","tid":1078077,"uid":119494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"神風"},{"pid":"b6c96e44b17c837a0ce2871